            "details": {
              "messages": {
                "default": [
                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to start a client meeting.\nYou will learn to greet the client and share the agenda.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/10cc53d1-2098-4c32-b54d-26350428a6c6-client-meeting-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "First, greet the client and say what the meeting is about.\nUse: 'Thanks for joining, [name]. Today we'll cover [topic].'\nExample: 'Thanks for joining, Sharma. Today we'll cover the app redesign progress.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/10cc53d1-2098-4c32-b54d-26350428a6c6-client-meeting-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Cool!",
                    "text": "Next, share the agenda with the client.\nUse: 'Let me share the agenda. [point 1], [point 2], and [point 3].'\nExample: 'Let me share the agenda. Timeline, budget, and next steps.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/10cc53d1-2098-4c32-b54d-26350428a6c6-client-meeting-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "You can also share the goal of the meeting.\nUse: 'The goal of this meeting is to [objective].'\nExample: 'The goal of this meeting is to finalize the feature list.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/10cc53d1-2098-4c32-b54d-26350428a6c6-client-meeting-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Let's practice opening a client meeting and setting the agenda!",
                    "media": null
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
